# Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online resources, which may not cover all perspectives or the latest developments in the field. Additionally, the interpretation of these concepts can vary across different cultural and organizational contexts, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed. Further research, including expert interviews and case studies, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of these differences.